reviews.review_text: I love using these squashes. I used them to replace potatoes in my stews. They are light to eat, and absorbs the flavor from the spices I use easily. The price is a good value.
Good quality, vegetable tasty fresh from the store affordable and fast delivery. Highly recommended.
